```

**Common log patterns:**

**Connection Successful:**
```
[INFO] vault-mcp: Connected to https://vault.shopify.io/mcp
[INFO] vault-mcp: Available tools: 14
```

**Authentication Error:**
```
[ERROR] vault-mcp: 401 Unauthorized
[ERROR] vault-mcp: Invalid or expired token
```
→ Token expired. Jump back to Requirement 2 to get fresh token.

**Network Error:**
```
[ERROR] vault-mcp: Failed to connect to vault.shopify.io
[ERROR] vault-mcp: Connection timeout
```
→ Network connectivity issue. Test: `curl -I https://vault.shopify.io/mcp`

**Token Format Error:**
```
[ERROR] vault-mcp: 400 Bad Request
[ERROR] vault-mcp: Malformed Authorization header
```
→ Missing "Bearer " prefix. Jump back to Requirement 2.

